data.name: Preset Message 1
data.message: “Great puppet masters think alike, I suppose.”

data.name: Preset Message 2
data.message: “Art is something that lasts for all posterity. Art is eternal.”

data.name: Preset Message 3
data.message: “True beauty lies in things that last forever, never rotting or fading.”

data.name: Preset Message 4
data.message: “The spider needs to be swifter than the fly.”

data.name: Preset Message 5
data.message: “For my name to be known all the way down to a kid like you… is an honour.”

data.name: Preset Message 6
data.message: “Since I don't like to wait or make people wait… I'll end this quickly.”
